him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20is%20examining%20documents%20linked%20to%20these%20assets%20and%20digital%20devices%20as%20part%20of%20its%20investigation%20into%20alleged%20financial%20irregularities%20in%20the%20hospital%2C%20which%20came%20into%20focus%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20a%2031-year-old%20doctor's%20rape%20and%20murder%20on%20August%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20agency%20suspects%20that%20Dr%20Ghosh%20and%20his%20wife%20bought%20these%20properties%20with%20proceeds%20of%20crime.%20%26quot%3BThese%20documents%20related%20to%20properties%20were%20seized%20based%20on%20the%20prima%20facie%20suspicion%20that%20those%20properties%20were%20purchased%20out%20of%20Proceeds%20of%20Crime%2C%26quot%3B%20ED%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20has%20found%20that%20Sangeeta%20Ghosh%20bought%20two%20properties%20without%20proper%20approval%20from%20West%20Bengal%20government%20and%20was%20later%20granted%20a%20post%20facto%20approval%20by%20none%20other%20than%20Dr%20Sandip%20Ghosh%2C%20her%20senior%20at%20work%20during%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20search%2C%20it%20was%20unravelled%20that%20Dr.%20Sangeeta%20Ghosh%20w%2Fo%20Dr%20Sandip%20Ghosh%2C%20had%20purchased%20two%20immovable%20properties%20without%20any%20proper%20approval%20from%20the%20State%20Government%20Authorities.%20Interestingly%2C%20a%20post%20facto%20approval%20was%20granted%20to%20Dr.%20Sangeeta%20Ghosh%20to%20purchase%20the%20property%20by%20Dr.%20Sandip%20Ghosh%20in%20year%202021.%20During%20this%20period%2C%20Dr.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandip%20Ghosh%20was%20posted%20in%20capacity%20of%20Principal%20of%20R.%20G.%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Dr.%20Sangeeta%20Ghosh%20was%20posted%20there%20as%20an%20Assistant%20Professor%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ED%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20on%20Friday%20searched%20seven%20premises%20belonging%20to%20Dr%20Ghosh%2C%20his%20close%20relatives%20and%20associates.%20The%