RS%20%20%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F58d512b85124c95b78f06ec3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22532%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENovo%20Nordisk's%20Saxenda%20helped%20children%20lose%20weight%20in%20a%2056-week%20trial.%3Cp%3EThomson%20Reuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENovo%20Nordisk's%20Saxenda%20helped%20children%20reduce%20their%20BMI%20by%205.8%25%20in%20a%2056-week%20trial.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThere%20are%20no%20approved%20obesity%20medications%20for%20children%20but%20Saxenda%20is%20approved%20for%20teens%20and%20adults.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFDA%20approval%20for%20children's%20weight%20loss%20drugs%20could%20open%20a%20new%20market%20for%20Novo%20Nordisk.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnovo-nordisk-cut-prices-usa-obesity-drug-wegovy-double-demand-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDanish%20drugmaker%20Novo%20Nordisk's%3C%2Fa%3E%20weight%20loss%20drug%20Saxenda%20has%20helped%20children%20aged%20six%20to%2011%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweight-loss-glp-1-drugs-ozempic-wegovy-mounjaro-effects-future-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereduce%20their%20body%20mass%20index%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20trial%20results%20released%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20showed%20that%20the%20children%20receiving%20daily%20injections%20of%20Saxenda%20were%20able%20to%20cut%20their%20BMI%20by%205.8%25%20on%20average%20in%20the%2056-week%20trial%20%E2%80%94%20and%20by%207.4%25%20on%20average%20compared%20with%20the%20placebo%20group.%20BMI%20is%20a%20measure%20of%20fitness%20based%20on%20height%20and%20weight%2C%20though%20it's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbmi-is-bogus-best-way-to-tell-if-youre-a-healthy-weight-2016-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewidely%20seen%20as%3C%2Fa%3E%20an%20inaccurate%20predictor%20of%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweight-loss-drugs-for-kids-6-years-old-mounjaro-trial-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20no%20FDA-approved%3C%2Fa%3E%20medications%20for%20children%20with%20obesity.%20The%20agency%20approved%20Saxenda%2C%20which%20has%20the%20chemical%20name%20liraglutide%2C%20for%20teenagers%20in%202020%20and%20for%20adults%20in%202014.%20Novo%20will%20seek%20FDA%20approval%20for%20the%20drug%20for%20younger%20children%2C%20the%20company's%20head%20of%20development%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F83bfafb7-72a4-455f-8def-0caa959def3d%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20date%2C%20children%20have%20had%20virtually%20no%20options%20for%20treating%20obesity.%20They%20have%20been%20told%20to%20'try%20harder'%20with%20diet%20and%20exercise%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20lead%20researcher%20Claudia%20Fox%20at%20a%20meeting%20in%20Madrid%2C%20where%20the%20results%20of%20the%20study%20of%2082%20children%20were%20presented.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20medication%20can%20allow%20children%20with%20obesity%20to%20live%20healthier%20and%20more%20productive%20lives%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENovo%20Nordisk's%20American%20rival%2C%20Eli%20Lilly%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweight-loss-drugs-for-kids-6-years-old-mounjaro-trial-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20also%20been%20testing%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparents-are-putting-their-kids-on-weight-loss-drugs-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eobesity-beating%20drugs%20for%20children%20%3C%2Fa%3Eas%20young%20as%20six.%20Novo%20Nordisk%20is%20the%20drugmaker%20behind%20the%20blockbuster%20medications%20Ozempic%20and%20Wegovy%2C%20while%20Eli%20Lilly%20produces%20Mounjaro%20and%20Zepbound.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWegovy%20and%20similar%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-cracks-down-on-ozempic-content-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edrugs%20for%20weight%20loss%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20become%20a%20huge%20business.%20The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstacks.cdc.gov%2Fview%2Fcdc%2F106273%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EUS%20adult%20obesity%20rate%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20about%2040%25%20from%202017%20to%202020%2C%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.goldmansachs.com%2Fintelligence%2Fpages%2Fanti-obesity-drug-market.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EGoldman%20Sachs%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0researchers%20estimated%20last%20year%20that%20the%20drugs%20could%20be%20prescribed%20to%2015%20million%20Americans%20by%202030.%20The%20bank's%20researchers%20said%20the%20anti-obesity%20drug%20market%20could%20grow%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.goldmansachs.com%2Fintelligence%2Fpages%2Fanti-obesity-drug-market.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%24100%20billion%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20drugs'%20success%20has%20made%20Novo%20Nordisk%20the%20most%20valuable%20company%20in%20Europe.%20Its%20stock%20is%20up%20over%2025%25%20year-to-date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b3771b30-588f-4b4d-9231-81903e6cdd49%5C%22%3EChildhood%20obesity%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20FDA%20approval%20on%20weight%20loss%20drugs%20for%20children%20could%20open%20up%20a%20new%20market%20for%20Novo%20Nordisk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Centers%20for%20Disease%20Control%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fobesity%2Fphp%2Fdata-research%2Fchildhood-obesity-facts.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DExpand%2520All-%2CAge%2C%2525%2520among%2520adolescents%252012%25E2%2580%259319.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20in%20five%20children%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20adolescents%20in%20the%20US%20have%20obesity%2C%20and%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatacenter.aecf.org%2Fdata%2Ftables%2F101-child-population-by-age-group%23detailed%2F1%2Fany%2Ffalse%2F2545%2C1095%2C2048%2C574%2C1729%2C37%2C871%2C870%2C573%2C869%2F62%2C63%2C64%2C6%2C4693%2F419%2C420%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enumber%20of%20children%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0ages%20six%20to%2011%20with%20obesity%20is%20about%206%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENovo's%20pricing%20for%20Ozempic%20and%20Wegovy%20has%20come%20under%20recent%20political%20scrutiny.%20In%20June%2C%20US%20Sen.%20Bernie%20Sanders%20announced%20that%20Novo%20Nordisk%20CEO%20Lars%20J%C3%B8rgensen%20would%20testify%20before%20the%20committee%20on%20September%2024%20at%20a%20hearing%20focusing%20on%20the%20prices%20that%20Novo%20Nordisk%20charges%20Americans%20for%20their%20drugs%2C%20Ozempic%20and%20Wegovy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESanders%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sanders.senate.gov%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2FLetter-from-Sen.-Bernard-Sanders-to-Novo-Nordisk.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvestigated%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20prices%2C%20saying%20that%20they%20are%20higher%20in%20the%20US%20than%20in%20other%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20highly-coveted%20drugs%20are%20being%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fozempic-celebrities-denied-semaglutide-wegovy-weight-loss-drugs-khloe-kardashian-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eused%20by%20celebrities%2C%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20including%20Oprah%20Winfrey%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-weight-loss-drug-wegovy-semaglutide-fit-ripped-healthy-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Charles%20Barkley%2C%20and%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fozempic-is-killing-keto-diet-report-suggests-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enon-celebrities%20%3C%2Fa%3Ealike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%2