ned%20politics%20by%20signing%20up%20with%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%2C%20claims%20that%20she%20received%20no%20support%20from%20PT%20Usha%2C%20although%20the%20latter%20claimed%20that%20she%20stood%20with%20the%20heartbroken%20wrestler%20during%20that%20tough%20time%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20what%20support%20I%20got%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Vinesh%20said%20during%20a%20chat%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FMahuaMoitraFans%2Fstatus%2F1833560474689884402%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elocal%20news%20channel%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BPT%20Usha%20madam%20visited%20me%20at%20the%20hospital.%20One%20photo%20was%20clicked...Like%20you%20said%2C%20in%20politics%20a%20lot%20happens%20behind%20closed%20doors.%20Similarly%2C%20politics%20happened%20there%20(in%20Paris)%20as%20well.%20That's%20why%20I%20was%20heartbroken.%20Otherwise%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20are%20saying%20'don't%20leave%20wrestling'.%20For%20what%20should%20I%20continue%3F%20There%20is%20politics%20everywhere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinesh%2C%20furious%20with%20PT%20Usha's%20decision%20to%20share%20the%20picture%20on%20social%20media%20claiming%20that%20she%20stands%20in%20support%20of%20the%20wrestler%2C%20said%20that%20this%20wasn't%20the%20right%20way%20to%20show%20support%2C%20and%20was%20mere%20pretension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20are%20on%20a%20hospital%20bed%2C%20where%20you%20don't%20know%20what's%20happening%20in%20life%20outside%2C%20you%20are%20going%20through%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20phases%20of%20your%20life.%20At%20that%20place%2C%20just%20to%20show%20everyone%20you%20are%20standing%20with%20me%2C%20aap%20bina%20bataye%20photo%20kheench%20rahe%20ho%2C%20fir%20social%20media%20pe%20daal%20ke%20bol%20rahe%20ho%20hum%20saath%20mein%20khade%20hain%20(clicked%20a%20photo%20without%20telling%20me%20and%20then%20putting%20it%20on%20social%20media%20to%20say%20you%20are%20standing%20with%20me).%20%26quot%3BThat's%20not%20how%20you%20show%20support%20(pretending%20to).%20What%20was%20it%20more%20than%20(posturing)!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726031340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Frctmhudg_pt-usha-vinesh_625x300_11_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fclicked-picture-without-telling-me-pretended-to-support-vinesh-phogat-slams-pt-usha-6538128%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20wrestler-turned-politician%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20has%20slammed%20IOA%20president%20PT%20Usha%20for%20'pretending'%20to%20support%20her%20after%20the%20failed%20weigh-in%20incident%20in%20Paris%20Olympics.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fclicked-picture-without-telling-me-pretended-to-support-vinesh-phogat-slams-pt-usha-6538128%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20Said%20On%20PM%20Modi's%20Stand%20On%20Major%20Foreign%20Policy%20Issues%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELeader%20of%20Opposition%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20indicated%20that%20the%20Congress%20party%20is%20in%20alignment%20with%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20major%20foreign%20policy%20issues%20like%20the%20relationship%20with%20the%20US%2C%20no%20talks%20with%20Pakistan%20unless%20the%20flow%20of%20terrorism%20is%20stopped%2C%20concerns%20over%20extremist%20elements%20in%20Bangladesh%20and%20Israel.%20However%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%2C%2054%2C%20was%20not%20in%20sync%20with%20PM%20Modi's%20policies%20on%20China%2C%20as%20he%20alleged%20that%20Chinese%20troops%20had%20taken%20control%20over%20Indian%20territory%20in%20Ladakh%20the%20size%20of%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20press%20conference%20held%20on%20Tuesday%20at%20the%20prestigious%20National%20Press%20Club%20here%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwe-wer