onicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Tables%20Turned%20Between%20Biden%20vs%20Trump%20And%20Harris%20vs%20Trump%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2028%2C%20shortly%20after%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20Donald%20Trump%20faced%20off%20in%20a%20Presidential%20debate%20for%20the%20high-stakes%20US%20election%2C%20many%20concluded%20that%20the%20fight%20was%20over%20even%20before%20it%20began.%20As%20the%2081-year-old%20US%20President%20lost%20his%20train%20of%20thought%20multiple%20times%20while%20speaking%20on%20critical%20subjects%2C%20his%2078-year-old%20predecessor%20and%20opponent%20mocked%20his%20confusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECut%20to%20September%2011%2C%20Trump%20faced%20a%20different%20Democrat%20presidential%20candidate.%20And%20this%20time%2C%20he%20was%20the%20older%20one%20and%20by%20a%20much%20larger%20margin.%20At%2059%2C%20Vice-President%20Kamala%20Harris%20is%20nearly%20two%20decades%20younger%20and%20she%20did%20not%20miss%20an%20opportunity%20to%20drive%20this%20point%20home%2C%20albeit%20in%20a%20subtle%20manner.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20I%20do%20offer%20is%20a%20new%20generation%20of%20leadership%20for%20our%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20US%20Presidential%20debates%2C%20televised%20and%20followed%20closely%20on%20social%20media%2C%20optics%20matter.%20Where%20Biden%20had%20appeared%20pale%20and%20confused%2C%20Harris%20was%20confident%20and%20focused.%20Harris%20started%20by%20walking%20up%20to%20Trump%20and%20shaking%20his%20hand%2C%20%26quot%3BHi%2C%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20let's%20have%20a%20good%20debate%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20This%20was%20the%20first%20handshake%20on%20the%20US%20Presidential%20debate%20stage%20after%20eight%20years.%20It%20was%20underlined%20that%20this%20was%20the%20first%20time%20the%20two%20leaders%20met.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20debate%20began%2C%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20Indian%20origin%20pulled%20no%20punches.%20On