2C%20they're%20eating%20the%20cats.%20They're%20eating%20the%20pets%20of%20the%20people%20that%20live%20there.%20And%20this%20is%20what's%20happening%20in%20our%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Harris'%20microphone%20was%20off%2C%20but%20she%20was%20seen%20laughing%20and%20mouthing%20%26quot%3Bwhat%3F%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20sharp%20response%20was%20when%20Harris%2C%20speaking%20about%20the%20Ukraine%20war%2C%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BPutin%20would%20be%20sitting%20in%20Kyiv%20with%20his%20eyes%20on%20the%20rest%20of%20Europe%26quot%3B%20if%20Trump%20was%20President.%20She%20also%20said%20Putin%20%26quot%3Bwould%20eat%20you%20for%20lunch%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompare%20these%20exchanges%20to%20the%20ones%20during%20the%20Biden%20vs%20Trump%20debate.%20The%20older%20President%20appeared%20to%20be%20putting%20up%20a%20relatively%20muted%20performance%20and%20struggling%20to%20articulate%20himself%20as%20Trump%20put%20out%20fireworks.%20The%20debate%20was%20still%20underway%20when%20the%20White%20House%20said%20Biden%20was%20suffering%20from%20a%20cold.%20The%20US%20President's%20performance%20did%20not%20help%20his%20attempts%20to%20convince%20the%20nation%20that%20he%20could%20serve%20in%20what%20is%20among%20the%20world's%20most%20powerful%20positions%20till%2086.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BYou%20are%20not%20running%20against%20Biden%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20key%20challenge%20Harris%20faced%20going%20into%20this%20debate%20was%20Team%20Trump's%20push%20to%20tie%20her%20to%20the%20Biden%20administration's%20failure.%20Harris%2C%20however%2C%20responded%20by%20stressing%20that%20she%20represents%20a%20new%20generation%20of%20leadership%20and%20that%20it's%20time%20to%20%26quot%3Bturn%20the%20page%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20clearly%20not%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20certainly%20not%20Donald%20Trump.%20And%20what%20I%20do%20offer%20is%20a%20new%20generation%20of%20leadership%20for%20our%20country%2C%20one%20who%20believes%20in%20what%20is%20possible.%20One%20who%20brings%20a%20sense%20of%20optimism%20about%20what%20we%20can%20do%20instead%20of%20always%20disparaging%20the%20American%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20another%20point%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20heard%20tonight%2C%20two%20very%20different%20visions%20for%20this%20country.%20One%20that%20is%20focused%20on%20the%20future%20and%20one%20that%20is%20focused%20on%20the%20past.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20managed%20to%20irk%20Trump%20by%20saying%20that%20world%20leaders%20laughed%20at%20him%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%20a%20disgrace%26quot%3B.%20Trump%20responded%20by%20citing%20close%20ties%20with%20Hungary%20Prime%20Minister%20Viktor%20Orban%20and%20that%20he%20has%20said%20Trump%20should%20return%20as%20President.%20The%20reference%20to%20Orban%2C%20known%20for%20restrictions%20on%20immigration%20and%20gay%20rights%2C%20was%20widely%20seen%20as%20Trump's%20continuing%20admiration%20of%20autocratic%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20was%20no%20specific%20mic%20drop%20moment%2C%20the%20debate%20did%20see%20several%20of%20Harris'%20punches%20land%20well.%20The%20November%20election%20is%20still%20likely%20to%20be%20a%20close%20contest%20--%20ABC%20poll%20tracker%20shows%20a%202.8%20percentage%20points%20--%20but%20the%20Democrats%20have%20without%20doubt%20made%20a%20comeback%20from%20where%20they%20were%20during%20the%20June%2028%20Biden%20vs%20Trump%20debate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726030980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fmqfp33jg_trump-harris-biden-split_625x300_11_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-presidential-debate-kamala-harris-donald-trump-how-tables-turned-between-biden-vs-trump-and-harris-vs-trump-6538351%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20June%2028%2C%20shortly%20after%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20Donald%20Trump%20faced%20off%20in%20a%20Presidential%20debate%20for%20the%20high-stakes%20US%20election%2C%20many%20concluded%20that%20the%20fight%20was%20over%20even%20before%20it%20began%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-presidential-debate-kamala-harris-donald-trump-how-tables-turned-between-biden-vs-trump-and-harris-vs-trump-6538351%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Girl%20Genitalia%20Mutilated%2C%20Sold%20For%20Magic%20In%20Ivory%20Coast%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20was%20a%20witch%20doctor%2C%20Moussa%20Diallo%20would%20regularly%20smear%20himself%20in%20a%20lotion%20made%20from%20a%20clitoris%20cut%20from%20a%20girl%20subjected%20to%20female%20genital%20mutilation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20big%20chief%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20dominate%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20small%20but%20charismatic%20fiftysomething%20from%20northwest%20Ivory%20Coast.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20put%20it%20on%20my%20face%20and%20body%26quot%3B%20every%20three%20months%20or%20so%20%26quot%3Bfor%20about%20three%20years%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20Diallo%2C%20who%20asked%20AFP%20not%20to%20use%20his%20real%20name.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGenitalia%20cut%20from%20girls%20in%20illegal%20%26quot%3Bcircumcision%26quot%3B%20ceremonies%20is%20used%20in%20several%20regions%20of%20the%20West%20African%20country%20to%20%26quot%3Bmake%20love%20potions%26quot%3B%20or%20magic%20ointments%20that%20some%20believe%20will%20help%20them%20%26quot%3Bmake%20money%20or%20reach%20high%20political%20office%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20Labe%20Gneble%2C%20head%20of%20the%20National%20Organisation%20for%20Women%2C%20Children%20and%20the%20Family%20(ONEF).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20ground-down%20clitoris%20can%20sell%20for%20up%20to%20around%20%24170%20(152%20euros)%2C%20the%20equivalent%20of%20what%20many%20in%20Ivory%20Coast%20earn%20in%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiallo%20stopped%20using%20the%20functions%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20but%20regional%20police%20chief%20Lieutenant%20N'Guessan%20Yosso%20confirmed%20to%20AFP%20that%20dried%20clitorises%20are%20still%20%26quot%3Bvery%20sought%20after%20for%20mystical%20practices%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20is%20clear%20from%20extensive%20interviews%20AFP%20conducted%20with%20former%20faith%20healers%2C%20circumcisers%2C%20social%20workers%2C%20researchers%20and%20NGOs%2C%20that%20there%20is%20a%20thriving%20traffic%20in%20female%20genitalia%20for%20the%20powers%20they%20supposedly%20impart.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20are%20convinced%20the%20trade%20is%20hampering%20the%20fight%20against%20female%20genital%20mutilation%20(FGM)%2C%20which%20has%20been%20banned%20in%20the%20religiously%20diverse%20nation%20for%20more%20than%20a%20quarter%20of%20a%20century.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20that%2C%20one%20in%20five%20Ivorian%20women%20are%20still%20being%20cut%2C%20according%20to%20the%20OECD%2C%20with%20one%20in%20two%20being%20mutilated%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20north.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECut%20and%20mixed%20with%20plants%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20he%20had%20a%20crisis%20of%20conscience%20and%20decided%20to%20campaign%20against%20FGM%2C%20Diallo%20said%20he%20was%20often%20asked%20by%20the%20women%20who%20performed%20excisions%20around%20the%20small%20town%20of%20Touba%20to%20use%20his%20powers%20to%20protect%20them%20from%20evil%20spells.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFemale%20circumcision%20has%20been%20practised%20by%20different%20religions%20in%20West%20Africa%20for%20centuries%2C%20with%20most%20girls%20cut%20between%20childhood%20and%20adolescence.%20Many%20families%20consider%20it%20a%20rite%20of%20passage%20or%20a%20way%20to%20control%20and%20repress%20female%20sexuality%2C%20according%20to%20the%20UN%20Children's%20agency%20UNICEF%2C%20which%20condemns%20cutting%20as%20a%20dangerous%20violation%20of%20girls'%20fundamental%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20physical%20and%20psychological%20pain%2C%20cutting%20can%20be%20fatal%2C%20and%20lead%20to%20sterility%2C%20birth%20complications%2C%20chronic%20infections%20and%20bleeding%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20the%20loss%20of%20sexual%20pleasure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiallo%20would%20often%20accompany%20the%20women%20who%20do%20the%20cutting%20out%20into%20the%20forest%20or%20to%20a%20home%20where%20dozens%20of%20girls%20would%20be%20circumcised%2C%20often%20surrounded%20by%20fetishes%20and%20sacred%20objects.%20So%20it%20was%20relatively%20easy%20for%20the%20former%20faith%20healer%20to%20obtain%20the%20precious%20powder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20they%20would%20cut%20the%20clitorises%20they%20would%20dry%20them%20for%20a%20month%20or%20two%20then%20pound%20them%20with%20stones%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bblack%20powder%26quot%3B%20which%20was%20then%20sometimes%20mixed%20with%20%26quot%3Bleaves%2C%20roots%20and%20bark%26quot%3B%20or%20shea%20butter%20that%20is%20often%20used%20in%20cosmetics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20could%20then%20sell%20it%20for%20around%20%26quot%3B100%2C000%20CFA%20Francs%20(152%20euros)%20if%20the%20girl%20was%20a%20virgin%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3B65%2C000%20(99%20euros)%20if%20she%20already%20had%20a%20child%26quot%3B%20or%20barter%20it%20for%20goods%20and%20services%2C%20Diallo%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ex-witch%20doctor%20said%20he%20was%20able%20to%20get%20some%20of%20the%20powder%20recently%20--%20a%20mix%20of%20human%20flesh%20and%20plants%2C%20he%20believes%20--%20from%20a%20cutter%20in%20his%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAFP%20was%20shown%20the%20powder%20but%20was%20unable%20to%20analyse%20it%20without%20buying%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Organ%20trafficking'%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20circumcisers%20interviewed%20by%20AFP%20insisted%20that%20clitorises%20cut%20from%20girls%20are%20either%20buried%2C%20thrown%20into%20a%20river%20or%20given%20to%20the%20parents%2C%20depending%20on%20local%20custom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20one%20in%20the%20west%20of%20the%20country%20admitted%20some%20end%20up%20being%20used%20for%20magic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20people%20pretend%20they%20are%20the%20girls'%20parents%20and%20go%20off%20with%20the%20clitoris%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWitch%20doctors%20use%20them%20for%20%26quot%3Bincantations%26quot%3B%20and%20sell%20them%20afterwards%2C%20she%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20circumciser%20said%20some%20of%20her%20colleagues%20were%20complicit%20in%20the%20trade%2C%20%26quot%3Bgiving%20(genitalia)%20to%20people%20who%20are%20up%20to%20no%20good%26quot%3B%20for%20occult%20purposes.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMutilated%20when%20she%20was%20still%20a%20child%2C%20one%20victim%20told%20AFP%20that%20her%20mother%20warned%20her%20to%20bring%20home%20the%20flesh%20that%20had%20been%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trade%20is%20regarded%20as%20%26quot%3Borgan%20trafficking%26quot%3B%20in%20Ivorian%20law%20and%20is%20punishable%20--%20like%20FGM%20--%20with%20fines%20and%20several%20years%20in%20prison%2C%20said%20lawyer%20Marie%20Laurence%20Didier%20Zeze.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20police%20in%20Odienne%2C%20who%20are%20in%20charge%20of%20five%20regions%20in%20the%20country's%20northwest%2C%20said%20no%20one%20has%20ever%20been%20indicted%20for%20trafficking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20won't%20say%20anything%20about%20sacred%20practices%2C%26quot%3B%20lamented%20Lieutenant%20N'Guessan%20Yosso.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cutters%20themselves%20are%20both%20feared%20and%20respected%2C%20locals%20told%20AFP%2C%20often%20seen%20as%20prisoners%20of%20evil%20spirits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Just%20nuts'%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20clitoris%20cannot%20give%20you%20magical%20powers%2C%20it's%20just%20nuts%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20gynaecologist%20Jacqueline%20Chanine%20based%20in%20the%20country's%20commercial%20capital%20Abidjan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20the%20practice%20is%20still%20stubbornly%20widespread%20in%20some%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20according%20to%20researchers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDieudonne%20Kouadio%2C%20an%20anthropologist%20specialising%20in%20health%2C%20was%20presented%20with%20a%20box%20of%20the%20powder%20in%20the%20town%20of%20Odienne%2C%20150%20kilometres%20north%20of%20Touba.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20contained%20a%20dried%20cut%20organ%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20blackish%20powder%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20discovery%20was%20included%20in%20a%202021%20report%20for%20the%20Djigui%20Foundation%2C%20whose%20conclusions%20were%20accepted%20by%20the%20Ministry%20for%20Women.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%20in%20Denguele%20district%2C%20of%20which%20Odienne%20is%20a%20part%2C%20%26quot%3Bbuy%20clitorises%20and%20mix%20the%20powder%20with%20their%20seeds%20to%20increase%20the%20fertility%20of%20their%20fields%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20Nouho%20Konate%2C%20a%20Djigui%20foundation%20member%20who%20has%20been%20fighting%20FGM%20in%20the%20area%20for%2016%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20parents%20of%20young%20girls%20were%20%26quot%3Bgutted%26quot%3B%20when%20he%20told%20them%20of%20the%20trafficking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20south%20and%20in%20the%20centre%20west%20of%20the%20country%2C%20women%20use%20clitoris%20powder%20as%20an%20aphrodisiac%2C%20hoping%20to%20prevent%20their%20husbands%20from%20straying%2C%20said%20criminologist%20Safie%20Roseline%20N'da%2C%20author%20of%20a%202023%20study%20on%20FGM%20which%20also%20pointed%20to%20the%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20and%20her%20two%20co-authors%20discovered%20that%20blood%20from%20cut%20women%20was%20also%20being%20used%20to%20honour%20traditional%20gods.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20far%20from%20the%20only%20Ivorian%20folk%20remedies%20that%20use%20body%20parts%2C%20according%20to%20lawyer%20Didier%20Zeze.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMystic%20beliefs%20keep%20it%20going%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20mystic%20has%20a%20central%20place%20in%20daily%20life%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Ivory%20Coast%20--%20where%20Islam%2C%20Christianity%20and%20traditional%20animist%20beliefs%20co-exist%20--%20said%20the%20Canadian%20anthropologist%20Boris%20Koenig%2C%20a%20specialist%20in%20occult%20practices%20there.%20%26quot%3BIt%20touches%20every%20sphere%20of%20people's%20social%2C%20professional%2C%20family%20and%20love%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20and%20there%20is%20generally%20nothing%20illegal%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trade%2C%20however%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20reasons%20that%20FGM%20survives%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Ivory%20Coast%2C%20NGOs%20argue%2C%20where%20the%20rate%20of%20cutting%20is%20generally%20falling%20and%20is%20below%20the%20West%20African%20average%20of%2028%20per%20cent%2C%20according%20to%20the%20OECD.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20near%20Touba%2C%20the%20former%20witch%20doctor%20Diallo%20recalled%20how%20up%20to%2030%20women%20would%20be%20cut%20in%20a%20day%20in%20the%20places%20his%20magic%20protected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dry%20season%20between%20January%20to%20March%20was%20the%20favoured%20period%20for%20circumcisions%20when%20the%20hot%20Harmattan%20wind%20from%20the%20Sahara%20helps%20scars%20heal%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStaff%20at%20the%20region's%20only%20social%20work%20centre%20say%20the%20cutting%20is%20still%20going%20on%20but%20is%20hard%20to%20quantify%20because%20it%20never%20happens%20in%20the%20open.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20it%20goes%20on%20in%20secret%2C%20hidden%20behind%20traditional%20festivals%20which%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20practice%2C%20kept%20going%20they%20say%20by%20circumcisers%20from%20neighbouring%20Guinea%20--%20only%20a%20few%20kilometres%20away%20--