rris%20settled%20the%20issue%2C%20definitively.%20She%20walked%20over%20to%20Trump%20at%20his%20podium%2C%20extended%20her%20hand%20and%20introduced%20herself%20as%20%26quot%3BKamala%20Harris.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20disarming%20way%20for%20Harris%20to%20approach%20a%20man%20who%20had%20spent%20weeks%20insulting%20her%20race%20and%20gender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%2C%20the%20debate%20quickly%20settled%20into%20an%20expected%20groove.%20Harris%20swiftly%20painted%20herself%20as%20a%20forward-looking%20candidate.%20She%20predicted%20Trump%20at%20the%20debate%20would%20pull%20from%20the%20%26quot%3Bsame%20tired%20playbook.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20bunch%20of%20lies%2C%20grievances%20and%20name-calling%2C%26quot%3B%20Harris%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESPARRING%20ON%20THE%20ECONOMY%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20debate's%20opening%20minutes%2C%20Trump%20and%20Harris%20went%20to%20battle%20on%20one%20of%20the%20issues%20that%20are%20top%20of%20mind%20for%20voters%3A%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%20detailed%20the%20economic%20policies%20she%20has%20rolled%20out%20in%20recent%20weeks%2C%20which%20include%20a%20substantial%20tax%20credit%20for%20small%20start-ups.%20Trump%20focused%20his%20comments%20on%20tariffs%2C%20saying%20he%20would%20protect%20the%20American%20economy%20from%20unfair%20foreign%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20both%20sides%20got%20their%20jabs%20in%2C%20Harris%20got%20to%20speak%20first%20on%20a%20topic%20where%20she%20trails%20Trump%20in%20terms%20of%20voter%20trust.%20She%20appeared%20to%20force%20the%20former%20president%20onto%20his%20back%20foot%2C%20and%20Trump%20essentially%20played%20defence%20on%20one%20of%20his%20strongest%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20doesn't%20have%20a%20plan%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%2C%20after%20Harris'%20opening%20comments.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20Run%2C%20Spot%2C%20Run.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3C