ks%20before%20the%20United%20States%20goes%20to%20polls.%20In%20a%20fierce%20debate%20that%20saw%20both%20candidates%20indulge%20in%20a%20verbal%20duel%2C%20there%20were%20claims%20and%20counter-claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%2C%20which%20is%20the%20first%20such%20debate%20between%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Kamala%20Harris%20will%20most%20likely%20also%20be%20the%20only%20debate%20they%20take%20part%20in%20with%20just%20over%2050%20days%20to%20go%20for%20the%20election.%20The%20debate%20was%20televised%20on%20US'%20ABC%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETens%20of%20millions%20of%20Americans%20tuned%20in%20to%20understand%20better%20what%20each%20presidential%20candidate%20had%20to%20offer%20and%20what%20their%20respective%20visions%20are%20to%20steer%20their%20nation%20forward.%20US%2C%20being%20a%20country%20of%20immigrants%20and%20a%20major%20global%20power%2C%20also%20invokes%20interest%20of%20people%20living%20in%20other%20countries%2C%20millions%20of%20whom%20tuned%20in%20earlier%20today%20to%20witness%20the%20closely-contested%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Kamala%20Harris%20traded%20claims%20about%20each%20other's%20record%20in%20office%2C%20as%20well%20as%20their%20plans%20if%20they%20emerge%20victorious%20in%20the%20election.%20Some%20of%20these%20claims%20required%20fact-checks%20to%20give%20a%20clear%20picture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFACT-CHECK%201%20-%20THE%20ECONOMY%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20Americans%20were%20better%20off%20than%20they%20were%20four%20years%20ago%2C%20Kamala%20Harris%20did%20not%20give%20a%20direct%20answer.%20She%20accused%20Trump%20of%20leaving%20Democrats%20%26quot%3Bthe%20worst%20unemployment%20since%20the%20Great%20Depression.%26quot%3B%20This%20can%20be%20seen%20as%20misleading.%20Joblessness%20spiked%20at%2014.8%20per%20cent%20in%20April%202020%20as%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20shut%20down%20the%20US.%20By%20the%20time%20Trump%20left%20office%20unemployment%20was%206.4%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFACT-CHECK%202%20-%20INFLATION%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamala%20Harris%20said%20she%20would%20offer%20families%20a%20tax%20credit%20of%20up%20to%20%246%2C000%20for%20each%20eligible%20child%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20%2450%2C000%20tax%20deduction%20for%20small%20businesses%2C%20if%20elected%20president.%20She%20claimed%20that%20Donald%20Trump%20would%20favor%20billionaires%20and%20corporations%20over%20anyone%20else%2C%20and%20said%20the%20former%20president%20planned%20a%20sales%20tax%20that%20would%20hurt%20ordinary%20Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20countered%20this%20claim%20by%20saying%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20administration%20ushered%20in%20the%20highest%20inflation%20in%20US%20history%2C%20quoting%20figures%20of%2021%20per%20cent%20and%20as%20high%20as%2060%20per%20cent%20on%20some%20goods.%20This%20is%20false.%20Inflation%20currently%20stands%20at%202.9%20percent.%20Inflation%20did%20hit%20a%20high%20of%209.1%20percent%20under%20Biden%20in%202022.%20This%20was%20well%20below%20a%20historic%20high%20of%2023.7%20percent%20in%201920.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFACT-CHECK%203%20-%20IMMIGRATION%20AND%20'MIGRANT%20CRIME'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump%20falsely%20claimed%20that%20%26quot%3Bmillions%20and%20millions%26quot%3B%20of%20people%20from%20countries%20such%20as%20Venezuela%20%26quot%3Bfrom%20mental%20institutions%20and%20insane%20asylums%26quot%3B%20are%20entering%20the%20US%20and%20committing%20crimes.%20He%20also%20re-aired%20a%20baseless%20viral%20claim%20that%20migrants%20are%20eating%20pets%20in%20places%20including%20Springfield%2C%20Ohio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Springfield%2C%20they're%20eating%20the%20dogs%2C%20the%20people%20that%20came%20in%2C%20they're%20eating%20the%20cats.%20They're%20eating%20the%20pets%20of%20the%20people%20that%20live%20there.%20And%20this%20is%20what's%20happening%20in%20our%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20and%20local%20authorities%20say%20there%20are%20no%20credible%20reports%20of%20any%20such%20animal%20killings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViolent%20and%20property%20crimes%20in%20the%20US%20are%20near%20their%20lowest%20levels%20in%20decades%2C%20according%20to%20FBI%20data%20from%202022%2C%20the%20most%20recent%20year%20for%20which%20figures%20are%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20June%202023%20study%20found%20a%20decline%20in%20incarceration%20rates%20among%20immigrants%20from%20all%20regions%20since%201960.%20Other%20research%20has%20found%20migrants%20commit%20fewer%20violent%20crimes%20than%20US%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFBI%20statistics%20from%20the%20first%20three%20months%20of%202024%20also%20show%20a%2015%20percent%20decrease%20in%20violent%20and%20property%20crime%20year-over-year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIllegal%20immigration%20during%20Donald%20Trump's%20administration%20was%20higher%20than%20under%20President%20Barack%20Obama's%20two%20terms.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20during%20the%20Biden%20administration%2C%20illegal%20immigration%20reached%20a%20historic%20high.%20It%20has%20fallen%20since%20an%20executive%20order%20signed%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamala%20Harris%20said%20Donald%20Trump%20put%20politics%20above%20policy%20by%20ordering%20Republican%20lawmakers%20this%20summer%20to%20kill%20a%20bipartisan%20bill%20that%20would%20have%20toughened%20policies%20at%20the%20southern%20US%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFACT-CHECK%204%20-%20ABORTION%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump%2C%20who%20appointed%20three%20conservative%20judges%20to%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20overturned%20Roe%20vs%20Wade%2C%20the%20precedent%20that%20guaranteed%20abortion%20access%2C%20called%20Democrats%20%26quot%3Bradical%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20claiming%20vice%20presidential%20candidate%20Tim%20Walz%20supports%20%26quot%3Bexecution%20after%20birth%20-%20it's%20execution%2C%20no%20longer%20abortion%20-%20because%20the%20baby%20is%20born%20is%20okay%2C%20and%20that's%20not%20okay%20with%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20false.%20No%20state%20allows%20a%20baby%20to%20be%20killed%20after%20it%20is%20born.%20This%20is%20infanticide%2C%20which%20is%20illegal%20across%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDebate%20moderator%20Linsey%20Davis%20corrected%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20state%20in%20this%20country%20where%20it%20is%20legal%20to%20kill%20a%20baby%20after%20it's%20born.%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Harris%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BNowhere%20in%20America%20is%20a%20woman%20carrying%20a%20pregnancy%20to%20term%20and%20asking%20for%20an%20abortion.%20That%20is%20not%20happening.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamala%20Harris%20claimed%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20Donald%20Trump%20were%20to%20be%20reelected%2C%20he%20will%20sign%20a%20national%20abortion%20ban.%26quot%3B%20But%20the%20former%20president%20immediately%20replied%3A%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20signing%20a%20ban%2C%26quot%3B%20saying%20that%20the%20issue%20is%20with%20the%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFACT-CHECK%205%20-%20ON%20AFGHANISTAN%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump%20claimed%20that%20the%20United%20States%20%26quot%3Bleft%20%2485%20billion%26quot%3B%20worth%20of%20equipment%20in%20Afghanistan.%20This%20is%20False.%20The%20actual%20figure%20is%20much%20lower%20than%20what%20Trump%20claimed%20in%20the%20debate.%20When%20the%20Taliban%20toppled%20Afghanistan's%20civilian%20government%20in%202021%2C%20it%20inherited%20US's%20military%20hardware%20given%20to%20the%20then%20government.%20The%20US%20Congress%20was%20briefed%20that%20about%20%247%20billion%20of%20US%20military%20equipment%20remained%20in%20Afghanistan%20and%20in%20the%20Taliban's%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20Afghanistan%2C%20Kamala%20Harris%20said%20when%20he%20was%20president%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20had%20%26quot%3Binvited%20the%20Taliban%20to%20Camp%20David.%26quot%3B%20This%20is%20true%2C%20reported%20independent%20fact-checking%20agency%20%3Cem%3EPolitiFact%3C%2Fem%3E.%20In%20September%2C%202019%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20had%20said%20he%20was%20canceling%20a%20planned%2C%20secret%20meeting%20for%20peace%20talks%20with%20the%20Taliban%20at%20Camp%20David.%20In%20February%202020%2C%20the%20US%20government%20and%20the%20Taliban%20signed%20a%20deal%20to%20end%20the%20war%20in%20Afghanistan%20within%2014%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamala%20Harris%20said%20that%20Donald%20Trump%20%26quot%3Bnegotiated%20directly%20with%20a%20terrorist%20organisation%20called%20the%20Taliban.%20The%20negotiation%20involved%20the%20Taliban%20getting%205%2C000%20terrorists%20released.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20True.%20A%202020%20agreement%20between%20the%20United%20States%20and%20the%20Taliban%20called%20for%20the%20release%20of%20up%20to%205%2C000%20Taliban%20prisoners%20who%20were%20jailed%20by%20the%20Afghan%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22No%20follow%2C%20no%20index%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politifact.com%2Farticle%2F2024%2Fsep%2F10%2Fpresidential-debate-live-fact-check-harris-trump%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPolitiFact%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20news%20reports%20and%20statements%20from%20Afghanistan's%20president%20indicated%20that%20the%20release%20happened.%20Afghanistan%20officials%20said%20they%20freed%20the%20prisoners%20at%20the%20request%20of%20the%20US.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726029300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fgm36ndcc_donald-trump-kamala-harris-presidential-debate-reuters_625x300_11_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-presidential-debate-donald-trump-and-kamala-harris-trade-charges-here-are-the-fact-checks-6538125%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kamala%20Harris%20and%20Donald%20Trump%20participated%20in%20the%20US%20Presidential%20Debate%20today%2C%20exactly%20eight%20weeks%20before%20the%20United%20Sta