EWhile%20there%20is%20no%20rule%20that%20require%20the%20two%20candidates%20to%20shake%20hand%2C%20it%20does%20mark%20a%20gesture%20of%20civility%20ahead%20of%20what%20is%20usually%20a%20politically%20brutal%20face-off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high-stakes%20debate%20began%20with%20a%20fiery%20jab%20by%20the%2078-year-old%20Republican%20who%20called%20Harris%20a%20%26quot%3BMarxist%26quot%3B%20and%20claimed%20that%20she%20and%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20had%20allowed%20%26quot%3Bmillions%20of%20people%20pouring%20into%20our%20country%20from%20prisons%20and%20jails%2C%20from%20mental%20institutions%20and%20insane%20asylums.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%20jibed%20the%20former%20US%20president%20several%20time%20by%20calling%20him%20a%20%26quot%3Bconvicted%20felon%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3Bfriend%20of%20dictators%26quot%3B%20and%20saying%20that%20he%20used%20%26quot%3Brace%20to%20divide%20the%20American%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20Trump's%20own%20former%20White%20House%20security%20officials%20have%20called%20him%20a%20%26quot%3Bdisgrace.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BWorld%20leaders%20are%20laughing%20at%20Donald%20Trump%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crucial%20debate%20comes%20only%2056%20days%20before%20the%20election%20in%20what%20has%20been%20a%20narrow%20race%20to%20the%20White%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20presidential%20debate%20in%20June%20resulted%20in%20Joe%20Biden%20pulling%20out%20of%20his%20reelection%20campaign%20and%20nominating%20Harris%20to%20take%20his%20place%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlmost%20all%20polls%20have%20shown%20the%20two%20candidates%20in%20a%20tight%20neck-and-neck%20contest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20critical%20chance%20for%20the%20two%20rivals%20to%20battle%20it%20out%20before%20the%20US%20goes%20to%20vote%20on%20November%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726027500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fmju13e7o