and%20Trump%20shook%20hands%20after%20they%20were%20introduced%2C%20ending%20an%20eight-year%20streak%20of%20no%20handshakes%20on%20the%20presidential%20debate%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20this%20is%20also%20the%20first%20time%20the%20two%20leaders%20met%2C%20and%20Ms%20Harris%20made%20a%20point%20to%20introduce%20herself%20to%20Mr%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20to%20respond%20to%20a%20question%20on%20the%20economy%20and%20the%20cost%20of%20living%2C%20an%20issue%20high%20on%20voters'%20minds%2C%20Ms%20Harris%20spoke%20of%20her%20middle-class%20background%20and%20her%20plans%20to%20support%20families%20and%20small%20businesses%20if%20elected%20to%20the%20top%20post.%20Targeting%20Trump%2C%20she%20said%20he%20would%20provide%20tax%20cuts%20to%20%26quot%3Bbillionaires%20and%20big%20corporations%26quot%3B%20and%20also%20reminded%20the%20viewers%20of%20the%20condition%20he%20left%20the%20economy%20in%20when%20Joe%20Biden%20took%20over.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20Ms%20Harris%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDonald%20Trump%20has%20no%20plan%20for%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20debate%20heated%20up%2C%20Trump%20started%20targeting%20Harris%20on%20the%20Biden%20administration's%20record%20on%20immigration%2C%20she%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BYou're%20going%20to%20hear%20from%20the%20same%20old%20tired%20playbook%2C%20a%20bunch%20of%20lies%2C%20grievances%20and%20name-calling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet's%20talk%20about%20what%20Donald%20Trump%20left%20us.%20Donald%20Trump%20left%20us%20worst%20unemployment%20since%20the%20great%20depression.%20Donald%20Trump%20left%20us%20the%20worst%20public%20health%20epidemic%20in%20a%20century.%20Donald%20Trump%20left%20us%20the%20worst%20attack%20on%20our%20democracy%20since%20the%20Civil%20War.%20And%20what%20we%20have%20done%20is%20clean%20up%20Donald%20Trump's%20mess%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20Trump%20switched%20to%20a%20personal%20attack.%20%26quot%3BShe%20is%20a%20Marxist.%20Her%20father%20was%20a%20Marxist.%26quot%3B%20Harris%20was%20seen%20smiling%20throughout.%20The%20former%20President%20complained%20that%20he%20did%20not%20get%20enough%20credit%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20job%26quot%3B%20during%20the%20Covid%20pandemic.%20%26quot%3BWe%20did%20a%20phenomenal%20job%20with%20the%20pandemic%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoving%20to%20the%20key%20subject%20of%20abortion%2C%20Harris%20warned%20that%20Donald%20Trump%20will%20ban%20abortions%20if%20he%20returns%20as%20President.%20%26quot%3BShe%20is%20lying%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20replied.%20Trump%20appeared%20to%20be%20stumped%20by%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20he%20would%20veto%20a%20national%20abortion%20ban.%20He%20said%20such%20a%20law%20won't%20pass%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20focus%20shifted%20to%20immigration%2C%20Harris%20said%20Trump%20would%20be%20talking%20about%20this%20subject%20a%20lot.%20She%20invited%20people%20to%20attend%20Trump's%20rallies%20because%20it's%20%26quot%3Ba%20really%20interesting%20thing%20to%20watch%26quot%3B.%20She%20said%20at%20the%20former%20President's%20rallies%2C%20he%20talks%20about%20fictional%20characters%20like%20Hannibal%20Lecter%20and%20that%20people%20start%20leaving%20his%20rallies%20because%20they%20are%20bored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20livid%20Trump%20responded%20that%20no%20one%20goes%20to%20Harris'%20rallies.%20Trump%20then%20started%20talking%20about%20a%20social%20media%20conspiracy%20theory%20about%20Haitian%20immigrants%20eating%20dogs%20in%20Ohio.%C2%A0%26quot%3BIn%20Springfield%2C%20they're%20eating%20the%20dogs.%20The%20people%20that%20came%20in%2C%20they're%20eating%20the%20cats.%20They're%20eating%20-%20they're%20eating%20the%20pets%20of%20the%20people%20that%20live%20there.%26quot%3B%C2%A0This%20got%20a%20laugh%20out%20of%20Harris%20as%20she%20shook%20her%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Trump%20attacked%20the%20Joe%20Biden%20administration's%20record%20on%20crime%20control%2C%20Harris%20responded%20that%20the%20remarks%20were%20%26quot%3Bso%20rich%26quot%3B%20coming%20from%20someone%20criminally%20charged%20multiple%20times.%20Trump%20said%20the%20cases%20against%20them%20were%20an%20example%20of%20the%20weaponisation%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%20to%20target%20a%20political%20opponent.%20He%20then%20brought%20up%20the%20July%2013%20assassination%20attempt%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3BI%20probably%20took%20a%20bullet%20to%20the%20head%20because%20of%20the%20things%26quot%3B%20they%20(Democrats)%20have%20said%20about%20him.%20%26quot%3BThey%20talk%20about%20democracy%2C%20I'm%20a%20threat%20to%20democracy.%20They're%20the%20threat%20to%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20travelled%20the%20world%20as%20Vice-President%20of%20the%20United%20States.%20World%20leaders%20are%20laughing%20at%20Donald%20Trump.%20They%20say%20you%20are%20a%20disgrace%2C%26quot%3B%20Harris%20said%2C%20drawing%20a%20rant%20from%20the%20former%20President.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20in%20Gaza%2C%20Harris%20batted%20for%20a%20two-state%20solution.%20Trump%20said%20the%20situation%20would%20have%20never%20reached%20this%20point%20if%20he%20was%20President.%20He%20said%20Harris%20hates%20Israel%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Arab%20population%20in%20the%20region.%20The%20vice%20president%20responded%20that%20Trump's%20claims%20were%20not%20true%20and%20stressed%20her%20support%20for%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20exchange%20on%20the%20Ukraine%20war%2C%20Harris%20said%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20would%20be%20in%20Kyiv%20if%20Trump%20was%20president.%C2%A0Harris%20said%20Trump%20would%20%26quot%3Bgive%20up%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20face%20of%20pressure%20from%20Putin.%20%26quot%3BPutin%20would%20be%20sitting%20in%20Kyiv%20with%20his%20eyes%20on%20the%20rest%20of%20Europe%2C%20starting%20with%20Poland.%20How%20quickly%20you%20would%20give%20up%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20favour%20and%20what%20you%20think%20is%20a%20friendship%20with%20what%20is%20known%20to%20be%20a%20dictator%20who%20would%20eat%20you%20for%20lunch.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20he%20wants%20Ukraine%20to%20win%20its%20war%20against%20Russia%2C%20Trump%20did%20not%20have%20a%20direct%20answer%20but%20said%20he%20wants%20the%20war%20to%20stop.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20in%20the%20US'%20best%20interest%20to%20get%20this%20war%20finished.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Trump%20constantly%20brought%20up%20the%20Biden%20administration's%20failures%2C%20trying%20to%20tie%20Harris%20to%20them%2C%20the%20vice%20president%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%20not%20running%20against%20Biden.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20why%20he%20had%20questioned%20Harris's%20racial%20identity%2C%20Trump%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20care%20what%20she%20is.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20he%20had%20read%20that%20she%20was%20not%20Black.%20Harris%20calls%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Btragedy%26quot%3B%20that%20Trump%20tries%20to%20use%20racial%20identity%20to%20divide%20Americans.%20She%20said%20she%20is%20neither%20Biden%20nor%20Trump%20and%20represents%20a%20new%20generation%20of%20leadership.%20Trump%20responded%20that%20the%20current%20administration%20is%20%26quot%3Bdivisive%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726023360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fgcovjkpg_donald-trump-kamala-harris_625x300_11_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fharris-trump-face-off-for-first-time-in-key-us-presidential-debate-6537401%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Eight%20weeks%20before%20the%20United%20States%20votes%2C%20Republic%20presidential%20candidate%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20his%20Democrat%20opponent%20Kamala%20Harris%20are%20now%20facing%20off%20in%20the%20presidential%20debate.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canon