)%20high%20and%20about%2080%20centimetres%20(32%20inches)%20wide.%20It%20has%20an%20exit%20shaft%20used%20by%20the%20militants%2C%20below%20a%20children's%20room%20in%20a%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hostages%20had%20likely%20been%20held%20in%20the%20dank%20tunnel%2C%20where%20it%20is%20hard%20to%20breathe%20and%20to%20stand%20up%20straight%2C%20for%20some%20time%2C%20possibly%20weeks%2C%20Hagari%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%F0%9D%90%84%F0%9D%90%97%F0%9D%90%82%F0%9D%90%8B%F0%9D%90%94%F0%9D%90%92%F0%9D%90%88%F0%9D%90%95%F0%9D%90%84%20%F0%9D%90%85%F0%9D%90%8E%F0%9D%90%8E%F0%9D%90%93%F0%9D%90%80%F0%9D%90%86%F0%9D%90%84%3A%20IDF%20Spokesperson%2C%20RAdm.%20Daniel%20Hagari%2C%20reveals%20the%20underground%20terrorist%20tunnel%20where%20Hersh%2C%20Eden%2C%20Carmel%2C%20Ori%2C%20Alex%20and%20Almog%20were%20held%20in%20brutal%20conditions%20and%20murdered%20by%20Hamas.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fedlfi4lR8U%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fedlfi4lR8U%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20(%40IDF)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIDF%2Fstatus%2F1833557217913471348%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2010%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20version%20of%20the%20video%20with%20English%20narration%20shows%20Kalashnikov%20rifle%20magazines%2C%20bags%20containing%20plastic%20bottles%20filled%20with%20urine%20and%20a%20bucket%20in%20a%20hole%20that%20served%20as%20a%20toilet.%20Women's%20clothing%20is%20strewn%20on%20the%20ground.%20The%20Hebrew%20version%2C%20broadcast%20live%20on%20Israeli%20television%20channels%2C%20also%20shows%20a%20chess%20set.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReuters%20was%20not%20able%20to%20independently%20verify%20the%20location%20or%20the%20date%20when%20the%20video%20was%20filmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20troops%20were%20in%20the%20area%2C%20fighting%20Hamas%20militants%20above%20ground%20when%20the%20hostages%20were%20killed%2C%20Hagari%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20soldiers%20had%20not%20been%20attempting%20a%20rescue%20operation.%20The%20military%20did%20not%20have%20precise%20verified%20intelligence%20about%20the%20hostages'%20presence%20in%20the%20area%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20six%20dead%20hostages%20were%20two%20women%20and%20four%20men%20aged%20between%2023%20and%2040%2C%20five%20of%20whom%20were%20taken%20from%20the%20Nova%20dance%20festival%20attacked%20by%20militants%20on%20Oct.%207%20last%20year.%20One%20of%20them%20was%20a%20father%20whose%20baby%20was%20born%20after%20he%20was%20taken%20hostage.%20The%20killings%20have%20sparked%20outrage%20and%20an%20outpouring%20of%20grief%20in%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEfforts%20to%20secure%20a%20ceasefire%20in%20Gaza%20that%20would%20include%20a%20hostage%20release%20deal%20have%20faltered%2C%20with%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20trading%20blame%20for%20the%20deadlock.%20Mass%20protests%20last%20week%20demanded%20Israeli%20leaders%20do%20more%20for%20their%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas-led%20fighters%20took%20around%20250%20foreign%20and%20Israeli%20hostages%20when%20they%20burst%20into%20Israel%20on%20Oct.%207%20and%20killed%201%2C200%20people%2C%20according%20to%20Israeli%20tallies.%20Israel's%20offensive%20in%20Gaza%20has%20killed%20more%20than%2040%2C000%20Palestinians%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20100%20hostages%20remain%20in%20Gaza%2C%20at%20least%20a%20third%20of%20whom%20are%20believed%20dead.%20More%20than%20100%20hostages%20were%20released%20in%20return%20for%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20in%20November%20and%20eight%20have%20been%20rescued%20by%20Israeli%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726022220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2