dent%20Kamala%20Harris%20and%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20met%20for%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-harris-debate-strategy-close-election-response-matters-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20debate%20on%3C%2Fa%3E%20Tuesday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20high-stakes%20face-off%2C%20taking%20place%20at%20the%20National%20Constitution%20Center%20in%20Philadelphia%2C%20may%20be%20the%20two%20candidates'%20only%20debate%20of%20the%20election%20%E2%80%94%20they%20have%20not%20yet%20agreed%20to%20meet%20for%20a%20second%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F8pJrIOey7OQ%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22WATCH%20LIVE%3A%20Harris%20and%20Trump%20debate%20%E2%80%94%20PBS%20News%20simulcast%20of%20ABC%E2%80%99s%202024%20Presidential%20Debate%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20biggest%20takeaways%20from%20the%20debate%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221585a56a-e2c0-4631-a399-f90a203a5f29%5C%22%3EKamala%20Harris%20made%20a%20point%20to%20shake%20hands%20with%20Trump%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%20since%202016%2C%20the%20two%20presidential%20candidates%20shook%20hands%20on%20the%20debate%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20Harris%20who%20made%20the%20first%20move%2C%20crossing%20the%20stage%20toward%20Trump%20to%20greet%20him%20at%20the%20outside%20of%20the%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKamala%20Harris%2C%20good%20to%20debate%20with%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20vice%20president%20could%20be%20heard%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fce92f52-1655-4ac7-bd1a-797bedc68cd0%5C%22%3EHarris%20often%20sneered%20at%20Trump%20as%20he%20spoke%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20Harris%20campaign's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkamala-harris-donald-trump-debate-microphone-philadelphia-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20efforts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20each%20candidate's%20microphone%20remained%20muted%20while%20the%20other%20was%20speaking.%20But%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20the%20Vice%20President%20didn't%20communicate%20with%20viewers%20as%20Trump%20spoke.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarris%20could%20often%20be%20seen%20on%20the%20split-screen%20staring%20over%20toward%20Trump%20with%20a%20bewildered%20look%2C%20narrowing%20her%20eyes%20and%20shaking%20her%20head%20at%20times.%20When%20Trump%20dubbed%20her%20a%20Marxist%2C%20she%20even%20appeared%20to%20laugh%2C%20placing%20her%20hand%20on%20her%20chin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20choice%2C%20given%20the%20performative%20aspects%20of%20a%20high-stakes%20presidential%20debate.%20Harris%20is%20betting%20that%20showing%20active%20disdain%20for%20Trump%20will%20play%20well%20with%20viewers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e3112370-0f4f-4781-be4b-42d476ee97db%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHarris%20successfully%20baited%20Trump%20over%20his%20rallies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERoughly%2025%20minutes%20into%20the%20debate%2C%20Harris%20said%20something%20unusual%3A%20She%20urged%20viewers%20to%20attend%20one%20of%20Trump's%20rallies%2C%20noting%20that%20he%20often%20speaks%20of%20fictional%20characters%20while%20claiming%20that%20attendees%20often%20leave%20early.%20That%20visibly%20angered%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20don't%20go%20to%20her%20rallies%2C%20there's%20no%20reason%20to%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%2C%20claiming%20that%20Harris%20pays%20people%20to%20attend%20her%20rallies.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20don't%20leave%20my%20rallies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20that%20moment%20on%2C%20Trump's%20tone%20took%20a%20noticeable%20turn%2C%20with%20more%20frequent%20yelling%20a