s%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%2C%20on%2010%20September%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F311837%2Fengineer-quit-us-job-to-launch-villa-mart-mobile-mandi-farmer-suicides-fair-income%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWorld%20Suicide%20Prevention%20Day%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20observed%20to%20raise%20awareness%20and%20prevent%20suicides.%20This%20year%2C%20the%20theme%20set%20by%20the%20International%20Association%20for%20Suicide%20Prevention%20(IASP)%20is%20%E2%80%98Changing%20the%20Narrative%20on%20Suicide%E2%80%99%2C%20with%20a%20call%20to%20action%20to%20%E2%80%98Start%20the%20Conversation%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20goal%2C%20according%20to%20IASP%2C%20is%20to%20shift%20how%20people%20perceive%20suicide%20and%20encourage%20open%20conversations%20about%20suicidal%20behaviour%20among%20communities%2C%20governments%2C%20individuals%2C%20organisations%2C%20and%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Health%20Organization%20(WHO)%20reports%20that%20over%207%2C20%2C000%20people%20die%20by%20suicide%20each%20year%20globally.%20An%20equal%20or%20even%20greater%20number%20attempt%20to%20take%20their%20own%20lives.%20This%20highlights%20the%20critical%20importance%20of%20being%20alert%2C%20present%2C%20and%20supportive%20of%20loved%20ones%20who%20may%20be%20struggling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FInfographic-website-41-1725952202.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22What%20to%20do%20if%20someone%20contemplating%20suicide%20comes%20to%20you%20for%20help%3F%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FInfographic-website-41-1725952202.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FInfographic-website-41-1725952202-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FInfographic-website-41-1725952202-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FInfographic-website-41-1725952202-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FInfographic-website-41-1725952202-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-365298%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CListening%20is%20the%20most%20crucial%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Priyanka%20Varma%2C%20a%20psychologist%20at%20The%20Thought%20Company%20and%20consultant%20at%20Holy%20Family%20Hospital%20in%20Mumbai.%20With%20over%20a%20decade%20of%20experience%2C%20she%20specialises%20in%20working%20with%20young%20adults%20as%20they%20navigate%20a%20world%20beyond%20social%20media.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderstanding%20how%20to%20support%20someone%20with%20suicidal%20thoughts%20is%20critical%2C%20so%20we%20spoke%20with%20Priyanka%20to%20learn%20what%20steps%20we%20can%20take%20to%20help%20those%20who%20may%20be%20struggling%20with%20suicidal%20tendencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20aware%20of%20the%20warning%20signs%20in%20someone%20contemplating%20such%20an%20extreme%20step%20is%20important.%20It%E2%80%99s%20crucial%20to%20recognise%20that%20this%20is%20never%20a%20decision%20made%20lightly.%20It%20is%20often%20a%20final%2C%20desperate%20measure%20someone%20considers%20when%20they%20feel%20life%20is%20no%20longer%20worth%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Priyanka%2C%20this%20usually%20occurs%20when%20a%20person%20is%20struggling%20to%20cope%20with%20a%20significant%20change%20in%20their%20life.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20noticed%20that%20some%20of%20the%20symptoms%20include%20hopelessness%20and%20worthlessness.%20They%20feel%20trapped%20and%20question%20their%20sense%20of%20self-worth.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20feeling%20of%20unbearable%2C%20intense%20pain%2C%20where%20they%20wonder%20if%20there%20is%20anything%20good%20waiting%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%20that%20for%20some%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F305972%2Fraashi-thakran-lost-brother-to-suicide-mental-health-rehabilitation-helpline-watch-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuicide%20might%20be%20an%20act%20of%20impulse%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20for%20others%2C%20it%20might%20be%20planned.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20may%20never%20speak%20about%20it.%20Others%20might%20wrap%20up%20their%20paperwork%20including%20creating%20a%20will%20and%20adding%20nominations%20in%20all%20assets.%20They%20might%20have%20conversations%20relating%20to%20this%20with%20their%20loved%20ones.%20They%20will%20say%20their%20final%20goodbyes%20and%20write%20letters%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20must%20look%20out%20if%20a%20loved%20one%20had%20a%20significantly%20life-altering%20event%2C%20which%20they%20are%20struggling%20to%20cope%20with.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20person%20seems%20to%20be%20in%20significant%20distress%2C%20speak%20to%20them%20compassionately%20and%20handle%20them%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20love%20and%20care%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20mental%20health%20professional.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20do%20if%20someone%20contemplating%20suicide%20comes%20to%20you%20for%20help%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Col%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EListen%20to%20them%20sans%20judgement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20most%20important%2C%20stresses%20Priyanka.%20%E2%80%9CTell%20them%20that%20I%E2%80%99m%20here%20for%20you%20and%20I%20want%20to%20hear%20what%20you%20say.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20judge%20them.%20Reassure%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%222%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon%E2